description: Sino Bioenergy Corp. investment and development of renewable energy. The company processes municipal household waste, construction waste, kitchen waste, and sludge to produce and sell organic, as well as mixed organic and inorganic fertilizers. It provides biomass energy production. The company was formerly known as Sino Fibre Communications, Inc. and changed its name to Sino Bioenergy Corp. in December 2010. Sino Bioenergy Corp. was incorporated in 1999 and is based in Hong Kong.
